{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-all-timeline-js","path":"/2015/02/26/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"allAwesomeItem":{"nodes":[{"awesomeListRepo":"phanan/htaccess","categoryHTML":"<h2>Miscellaneous</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>Force Downloading</h3>\n<p>Sometimes you want to force the browser to download some content instead of displaying it.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-apacheconf\">&#x3C;Files *.md>\n    ForceType application/octet-stream\n    Header set Content-Disposition attachment\n&#x3C;/Files>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Now there is a yang to this yin:</p>","updatedAt":"2015-02-26T14:41:40.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"phanan/htaccess","categoryHTML":"<h2>Miscellaneous</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>Prevent Downloading</h3>\n<p>Sometimes you want to force the browser to display some content instead of downloading it.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-apacheconf\">&#x3C;FilesMatch \"\\.(tex|log|aux)$\">\n    Header set Content-Type text/plain\n&#x3C;/FilesMatch>\n</code></pre>","updatedAt":"2015-02-26T14:41:40.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"phanan/htaccess","categoryHTML":"<h2>Miscellaneous</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>Allow Cross-Domain Fonts</h3>\n<p>CDN-served webfonts might not work in Firefox or IE due to <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cross-origin_resource_sharing\">CORS</a>. This snippet solves the problem.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-apacheconf\">&#x3C;IfModule mod_headers.c>\n    &#x3C;FilesMatch \"\\.(eot|otf|ttc|ttf|woff|woff2)$\">\n        Header set Access-Control-Allow-Origin \"*\"\n    &#x3C;/FilesMatch>\n&#x3C;/IfModule>\n</code></pre>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/h5bp/server-configs-apache/issues/32\">Source</a></p>","updatedAt":"2015-02-26T14:41:40.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"phanan/htaccess","categoryHTML":"<h2>Performance</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>Turn eTags Off</h3>\n<p>By removing the <code>ETag</code> header, you disable caches and browsers from being able to validate files, so they are forced to rely on your <code>Cache-Control</code> and <code>Expires</code> header. <a href=\"http://www.askapache.com/htaccess/apache-speed-etags.html\">Source</a></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-apacheconf\">&#x3C;IfModule mod_headers.c>\n    Header unset ETag\n&#x3C;/IfModule>\nFileETag None\n</code></pre>","updatedAt":"2015-02-26T14:38:23.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"LewisJEllis/awesome-lua","categoryHTML":"<h3>Implementations, Interpreters, and Bindings</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/yuin/gopher-lua\">GopherLua</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/yuin/gopher-lua\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">5k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":5047,\"repo\":\"yuin/gopher-lua\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Lua 5.1 VM and compiler implemented in Go with Go APIs.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-02-26T04:59:50.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jbhuang0604/awesome-computer-vision","categoryHTML":"<h2>Software</h2><h4>Intrinsic Images</h4>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://people.tuebingen.mpg.de/mkiefel/projects/intrinsic/\">Recovering Intrinsic Images with a global Sparsity Prior on Reflectance</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-02-26T02:49:31.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jbhuang0604/awesome-computer-vision","categoryHTML":"<h2>Software</h2><h4>Intrinsic Images</h4>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://giga.cps.unizar.es/~elenag/projects/EGSR2012_intrinsic/\">Intrinsic Images by Clustering</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-02-26T02:49:31.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jbhuang0604/awesome-computer-vision","categoryHTML":"<h2>Software</h2><h4>Contour Detection and Image Segmentation</h4>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.mvdblive.org/seeds/\">SEEDS</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-02-26T02:45:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jbhuang0604/awesome-computer-vision","categoryHTML":"<h2>Software</h2><h4>Video Segmentation</h4>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.cse.buffalo.edu/~jcorso/r/supervoxels/\">Streaming hierarchical video segmentation</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-02-26T02:45:57.000Z"}]}},"pageContext":{"type":"day","from":1424908800000,"to":1424995199999,"previousId":"2015-02-27","nextId":"2015-02-25","nextName":"Feb 25th, 2015","previousName":"Feb 27th, 2015"}},"staticQueryHashes":["228695001","2744905544","2828988102"]}